   "body" : "I just ran bitcoind for the first time, and tried to exit with Ctrl+C.  It appeared to be stuck, so I killed the process.  Before I could start it again I had to delete the lock file.  However, later I found out bitcoind does handle sigint, and exits.\r\n\r\nIt would be nice if it displaced an \"Exiting...\" message so that you know it is busy exiting.",
